 state in HTe cannot be properly described within the mean-field\npicture of the BCS theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 Feb 2018 12:58:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Feb 2018 22:50:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 19 May 2018 20:06:01 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 23 Jan 2019 15:56:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-26"}
